items.badge_description: There's beer in them thar hills! You're setting off on your journey through the world of beer, but be sure to take a little time to get to know each brewery as you go. That's a beer from 35 different breweries. Try 5 more for Level 8!

Fresh from the tap is one of the best ways to enjoy a beer. Just try to use a glass and not drink directly from the tap, as tempting as it may be. That's 185 checkins with the serving style of Draft. Try 5 more for Level 38!
After a long day, what better way to kick back than with a crisp and refreshing lager? You're already feeling more relaxed, aren't you?. That's 205 different Lagers! Try 5 more to unlock Level 42.
